OL,6,FA long-awaited football investment
OL,7,Ffund is set to be delivered within the
OL,8,Fnext two years.
OL,10,FThe #36.2 million Northern Ireland
OL,11,FFootball Fund, formerly known as the
OL,12,Fsub regional stadia programme, will
OL,13,Fdeliver a National Training Centre as
OL,14,Fwell as funding for clubs.
OL,16,FIt comes more than a decade after the
OL,17,Ffund was first mooted in 2011.
