OL,3,CFootball investment fund set to be
OL,4,Cdelivered within the next two years
OL,6,FThe club investment strand of the fund
OL,7,Fis to open for applications in this
OL,8,Ffinancial year, with the awards
OL,9,Fexpected to be spent in the 2025/26
OL,10,Ffinancial year.
OL,12,FCommunities Minister Gordon Lyons
OL,13,Fconfirmed the release of the funding
OL,14,Fto football clubs from across Northern
OL,15,FIreland at the National Stadium
OL,16,FWindsor Park on Wednesday afternoon.
OL,18,FHe described the #36.2 million as an
OL,19,F"initial budget", adding he regards
OL,20,Fthis as a long-term programme with
OL,21,Ffurther funding needed in future years.
