OL,6,FHe said his department has costed need
OL,7,Ffor football facilities at #200
OL,8,Fmillion, adding he will continue to
OL,9,Fmake the case for additional funding.
OL,11,FMr Lyons termed the fund as a "once in
OL,12,Fa lifetime opportunity to transform
OL,13,Fthe game locally".
OL,15,F"For players at performance and
OL,16,Fgrassroots level I want to see better
OL,17,Ffacilities. I want to see improved
OL,18,Faccessibility for disadvantaged and
OL,19,Funderrepresented groups, both as
OL,20,Fparticipants and supporters," he said.
