OL,6,F"I want fans now, and in the future,
OL,7,Fto have the best experience at their
OL,8,Flocal club. And looking forward, I
OL,9,Fwant to foster our footballing stars
OL,10,Fof the future with the creation of a
OL,11,FNational Training Centre.
OL,13,F"I am committed to fully utilising the
OL,14,F#36.2 million and to seeking to
OL,15,Fsustain the fund with further
OL,16,Finvestment from the Executive, from
OL,17,Fwithin the football sector and from
OL,18,Facross local government."
