OL,4,Cdelivered within the next two years
OL,6,F"Work is progressing at pace on a
OL,7,FNational Training Centre for Football
OL,8,Fto host elite training for our
OL,9,Fnational men's, women's and youth
OL,10,Fteams and to drive skills for people
OL,11,Finvolved at all levels of the game. I
OL,12,Fwill be saying more on this in coming
OL,13,Fweeks," he said.
OL,15,F"Over the last 100 days, I have
OL,16,Fvisited clubs and community football
OL,17,Ffacilities across Northern Ireland. I
OL,18,Frecognise the passion and benefits
OL,19,Fthis sport brings to so many people.
