OL,4,Cdelivered within the next two years
OL,6,F"I know the long delay has been a
OL,7,Fsource of frustration for clubs and
OL,8,Flocal communities.
OL,10,F"I am committed to delivering long-
OL,11,Fterm investment in football and I am
OL,12,Fdetermined to secure additional
OL,13,Ffunding in future years to make this
OL,14,Fhappen. I look forward to continuing
OL,15,Fto work with clubs, the Irish FA and
OL,16,Fthe Northern Ireland Football League
OL,17,Fto ensure clubs are accessible with
OL,18,Fhigh quality facilities, welcoming to
OL,19,Fall and that we secure a sustainable
OL,20,Ffootballing future for the generations
OL,21,Fto come."
